## Build Output
The production build completed successfully:
- 6 routes generated (/, /about, /addresses, /faq, /support, /_not-found)
- All pages compiled without errors or warnings
- First Load JS size: ~102-112 kB
- Build time: ~8.2 seconds

## Next Steps for User

To enable Web Analytics on Vercel:
1. Deploy this project to Vercel (using `vercel deploy` or push to connected Git repository)
2. Navigate to the Vercel Dashboard → Analytics section
3. Click "Enable" button to activate Web Analytics for the project
4. After deployment, verify tracking works by checking browser Network tab for requests to `/<unique-path>/view`

